'''2015年沙那清真寺爆炸案'''，是指發生於2015年3月20日，在[[葉門|葉門]][[薩那省|薩那省]][[沙那|沙那]]的連環爆炸案<ref name="albawaba" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/20/us-yemen-attack-bomb-idUSKBN0MG11J20150320|title=Death toll rises to 87 in Yemen mosque bombings: medical source|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2015-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322061310/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/20/us-yemen-attack-bomb-idUSKBN0MG11J20150320|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當地的巴德尔（al-Badr）和阿尔哈斯（al-Hashoosh）兩座[[清真寺|清真寺]]，於[[中午|中午]]的{{link-en|晌禮祈禱|Zuhr prayer}}時受到[[自殺攻擊|自殺炸彈攻擊]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-31983627|title=Yemen crisis: Suicide attacks hit Sana'a Houthi mosques|publisher=BBC|date=20 March 2015|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321100441/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-31983627|dead-url=no}}</ref>。爆炸總共造成了至少142人死亡，與351人受傷<ref name="alJazeera"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/20/yemen-suicide-bombings-sanaa-mosques-shia-huthi-muslims-scores-dead |title="Yemen: over 100 dead in suicide bombings at Houthi mosques in Sana'a", by ''The Guardian'' |accessdate=2015-03-21 |archive-date=2015-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321124842/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/mar/20/yemen-suicide-bombings-sanaa-mosques-shia-huthi-muslims-scores-dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

